.html|accessdate=2020-10-02|author=Collins|date=2020-10-02|first=Kaitlin|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002135112/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/10/02/politics/ronna-mcdaniel-coronavirus/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite tweet|title=Ronna McDaniel has tested positive for coronavirus. She found out Wednesday and has been home since the previous Saturday, according to statement from Republican National Committee.|user=MichaelCBender|number=1312022856239394819|date=2020-10-02|access-date=2020-10-02}}</ref>。10月2日，特朗普在[[沃尔特·里德国家军事医疗中心|沃尔特·里德国家军事医疗中心]]住院<ref name="auto">{{Cite news|author=Liptak|first=Kevin|date=2020-10-02|title=Trump taken to Walter Reed medical center and will be hospitalized 'for the next few days'|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/02/politics/president-donald-trump-walter-reed-coronavirus/index.html|accessdate=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002213225/https://www.cnn.com/2020/10/02/politics/president-donald-trump-walter-reed-coronavirus/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Subramanian|first=Courtney|author2=Jackson|first2=David|date=2020-10-02|title=President Trump taken to Walter Reed hospital for an expected stay of a few days after COVID-19 diagnosis|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/10/02/trump-heads-walter-reed-hospital-after-positive-covid-19-test/5894256002/|accessdate=2020-10-03|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003005621/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/10/02/trump-heads-walter-reed-hospital-after-positive-covid-19-test/5894256002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 玫瑰园提名仪式 ==
[[File:President_Trump_Nominates_Judge_Amy_Coney_Barrett_for_Associate_Justice_of_the_U.S._Supreme_Court_(50397097478).jpg|left]]为最高法院大法官]]
2020年9月26日，[[露絲·貝德·金斯堡|露絲·貝德·金斯堡]]去世后，{{le|白宫玫瑰花园|White House Rose Garden}}举行仪式，提名[[艾米·科尼·巴雷特|艾米·科尼·巴雷特]]为[[美國最高法院大法官|最高法院大法官]]。该活动的大多数参与者都没有佩戴口罩，也没有[[保持社交距离|保持社交距离]]。接下来的一周内，至少有七名参与者的检测结果呈阳性：特朗普夫妻、[[霍普·希克斯|霍普·希克斯]]、比尔·斯蒂芬、迈克·李、詹静思和凯莉安·康威。李拍摄时没有佩戴口罩，且热情地拥抱与会者。在活动中，其中五人坐在前三排，并与其他[[共和黨_(美國)|共和党]]高级官员密切接触<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2020/10/02/trump-timeline-activities-425041|title=Where Trump went (and who he was with) leading up to his coronavirus diagnosis|website=POLITICO|accessdate=2020-10-03|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003080409/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/10/02/trump-timeline-activities-425041|dead-url=no}}</ref>。詹金斯后来发表声明：“我为我的判断失误感到遗憾，因为我在仪式中没有佩戴口罩，并与玫瑰园中的许多人握手。”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/scotus-nomination-coronavirus-superspreader-white-house-senator-mike-lee-b749466.html|title=White House SCOTUS announcement is suspected as Covid super-spreader event as video shows infected senator hugging attendees|date=2020-10-03|accessdate=2020-10-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004005353/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/scotus-nomination-coronavirus-superspreader-white-house-senator-mike-lee-b749466.html|archivedate=2020-10-04|dead-url=no|language=en}}</ref>

== 总统辩论 ==
9月29日，白宫人员参加了[[克利夫兰诊所|克利夫兰诊所]]举行的第一次{{le|2020年美国总统辩论|2020 United States presidential debates|总统辩论}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=11 positive coronavirus tests traced to presidential debate, Cleveland officials say|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/11-positive-coronavirus-tests-traced-presidential-debate-cleveland-officials-say-n1241841|accessdate=2020-10-02|author=Li|date=2020-10-02|first=David K.|publisher=NBC News|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003000828/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/11-positive-coronavirus-tests-traced-presidential-debate-cleveland-officials-say-n1241841|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至少有11个人参与了活动的准备过程，之后被测试为阳性<ref>{{Cite web|title=City of Cleveland announces 11 positive cases of COVID-19 stemming from preparations for presidential debate|url=https://www.wkyc.com/article/news/local/cleveland/cleveland-11-cases-after-presidential-debate/95-74828d32-8c97-4b24-81e5-209689df6a86|accessdate=2020-10-02|author=Staff|date=2020-10-02|publisher=WKYC Cleveland}}</ref>。

尽管早先宣称将对所有参与者进行测试，但辩论主持人[[克里斯·华莱士|克里斯·华莱士]]后来透露，特朗普及其随行人员来得太迟，无法接受测试，于是在“荣誉制度”下进入辩论厅。接下来几天，至少有三人被确诊：特朗普夫妻和霍普·希克斯<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cleveland.com/coronavirus/2020/10/president-trump-first-lady-and-hope-hicks-may-have-spread-coronavirus-at-cleveland-presidential-debate.html|title=President Trump, First Lady and Hope Hicks may have spread coronavirus at Cleveland presidential debate|date=2020年10月2日|website=cleveland|accessdate=2020年10月3日|archive-date=2020年10月3日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003232526/https://www.cleveland.com/coronavirus/2020/10/president-trump-first-lady-and-hope-hicks-may-have-spread-coronavirus-at-cleveland-presidential-debate.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。辩论前，双方均同意辩论委员会的要求，规定除两名总统候选人和辩论主持人外，所有与会者都要戴口罩。尽管如此，特朗普的听众中有几位客人，包括他的妻子、家人和高级职员，都没有佩戴口罩，违反了会场的安全规定。当克利夫兰诊所的工作人员亲自为特朗普的客人提供口罩时，他们再次拒绝遵守先前商定的口罩规定<ref name="ap-timeline">{{Cite news|title=Timeline of Trump’s activities in week coronavirus hit home|url=https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-virus-outbreak-joe-biden-donald-trump-melania-trump-294c95e21aad3d59d453a4b812a13278|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002084004/https://apnews.com/article/election-2020-virus-outbreak-joe-biden-donald-trump-melania-trump-294c95e21aad3d59d453a4b812a13278|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Rossman|first=Sean|author2=Cummings|first2=William|last3=Fritze|first3=John|last4=Jackson|first4=David|last5=Subramanian|first5=Courtney|title=Trump tweets video before going to Walter Reed hospital with COVID-19: live updates|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/10/02/trump-covid-19-updates-president-melania-trump-hicks-test-positive/3549616001|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2020-10-02|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003001216/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2020/10/02/trump-covid-19-updates-president-melania-trump-hicks-test-positive/3549616001/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Anderson|first=Chris|title=Some guests on President Trump's side of debate room reportedly refused masks when asked by Cleveland Clinic doctor|url=https://www.cleveland19.com/2020/09/30/some-guests-president-trumps-side-debate-room-reportedly-refused-masks-when-asked-by-cleveland-clinic-doctor/|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[WOIO|WOIO]]|date=2020-09-30|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002232732/https://www.cleveland19.com/2020/09/30/some-guests-president-trumps-side-debate-room-reportedly-refused-masks-when-asked-by-cleveland-clinic-doctor/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 初步检测 ==
9月30日，特朗普的顾问[[霍普·希克斯|霍普·希克斯]]测试呈阳性，并出现症状，被确诊为[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]。同日，RNC主席Ronna McDaniel也被诊断为2019冠状病毒病<ref name="cnn-ronna"/><ref>{{Cite news|author=Regan|first=Helen|title=White House officials knew Hicks tested positive -- but Trump still traveled for a fundraiser|url=https://www.cnn.com/world/live-news/coronavirus-pandemic-10-02-20-intl/h_da0bc1f63ac9a7ab1e5ea0a4135723b7|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2020-10-02|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002213401/https://www.cnn.com/world/live-news/coronavirus-pandemic-10-02-20-intl/h_da0bc1f63ac9a7ab1e5ea0a4135723b7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这两项诊断结果均没有立即公布。

白宫的官员最初试图隐瞒希克斯的诊断结果，特朗普继续执行他的常规时间表，参加了他在{{le|特朗普國家高爾夫俱樂部|Trump National Golf Club Bedminster}}组织的筹款活动<ref>{{Cite news|author=Moreno|first=J. Edward|title=White House wanted to keep Hope Hicks's positive COVID-19 test private: report|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/519304-white-house-staff-wanted-to-keep-hope-hicks-positive-covid-19-test|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[The_Hill|The Hill]]|date=2020-10-02|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003042358/https://thehill.com/homenews/administration/519304-white-house-staff-wanted-to-keep-hope-hicks-positive-covid-19-test|dead-url=no}}</ref>。希克斯和白宫因隐藏诊断结果而受到批评。希克斯的诊断结果最终于10月1日晚上宣布<ref>{{Cite news|author=Crump|first=James|title=Video shows covid-positive Hope Hicks touching Air Force One railing ahead of top aides like Kushner|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/hope-hicks-coronavirus-air-force-one-jared-kushner-trump-aides-b746987.html|date=2020-10-02|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004164159/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/hope-hicks-coronavirus-air-force-one-jared-kushner-trump-aides-b746987.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特朗普在接受[[福克斯新闻|福克斯新闻]]的采访时<ref name="sky-timeline">{{Cite news|title=Trump coronavirus: Timeline of US president's movements with wife Melania before testing positive for COVID-19|url=https://news.sky.com/story/trump-coronavirus-timeline-of-us-presidents-movements-with-wife-melania-before-testing-positive-for-covid-19-12087454|date=2020-10-02|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[Sky_News|Sky News]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201004164202/https://news.sky.com/story/trump-coronavirus-timeline-of-us-presidents-movements-with-wife-melania-before-testing-positive-for-covid-19-12087454|dead-url=no}}</ref>首次披露了这一结果，并宣布自己和第一夫人正在接受检测<ref name="ap-timeline"/><ref>{{Cite news|author=Calia|first=Mike|author2=Macias|first2=Amanda|title=Trump quarantines after top aide Hope Hicks tests positive for coronavirus|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/10/02/hope-hicks-coronavirus.html|date=2020-10-03|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=[[CNBC|CNBC]]|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201003000034/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/10/02/hope-hicks-coronavirus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。采访结束后，特朗普在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上确认了这一消息。此前，特朗普曾与希克斯一起乘坐[[空军一号|空军一号]]。

