ette.com/news/2020/11/07/Trump-s-aides-frustrated-after-Meadows-s-silence-on-infection/stories/202011070087 |website=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |publisher=[[匹兹堡邮报|匹兹堡邮报]] |accessdate=2020-11-09 |language=en |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116042032/https://www.post-gazette.com/news/2020/11/07/Trump-s-aides-frustrated-after-Meadows-s-silence-on-infection/stories/202011070087 |dead-url=no }}</ref>7日，佛罗里达州众议员[[馬特·蓋茨|馬特·蓋茨]]宣布自己新冠抗体检测结果为阳性，但并无任何新冠症状，也无活体病毒。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Broadwater |first1=Luke |title=Matt Gaetz, a congressman with close ties to the White House, said he tested positive for antibodies this week. |url=https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/11/07/world/covid-19-coronavirus-updates/matt-gaetz-a-congressman-with-close-ties-to-the-white-house-said-he-tested-positive-for-antibodies-this-week |website=The New York Times |publisher=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |accessdate=2020-11-07 |date=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2021-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116041944/https://www.nytimes.com/live/2020/11/07/world/covid-19-coronavirus-updates/matt-gaetz-a-congressman-with-close-ties-to-the-white-house-said-he-tested-positive-for-antibodies-this-week |dead-url=no }}</ref>

