== 影响 ==

=== 股市 ===
美国总统特朗普确诊感染新冠病毒消息一度引发全球金融市场动荡，美股期货也闻讯下跌，导致[[道琼斯工业平均指数|道琼斯工业平均指数]]在10月3日下跌超过300点，下跌幅度为1.29％，降至27,458.44点。[[标准普尔500指数|标准普尔500指数]]下跌1.36％，降至3,334.74点。[[納斯達克指數|纳斯达克指数]]也下跌1.82％，降至11,120.49点。同时也拖累欧洲股市跟着陪跌，英、法、德、意四大股市跌幅更是超过1%<ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普感染新冠病毒引发全球金融市场震荡 {{!}} DW {{!}} 02.10.2020|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E9%9C%87%E8%8D%A1/a-55132230|accessdate=2020-10-03|last=Welle (www.dw.com)|first=Deutsche|work=DW.COM|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116042115/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E9%9C%87%E8%8D%A1/a-55132230|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普夫妇感染新冠病毒 纽约股市下跌|url=https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/cai-jing/2020/10/03/te-lang-pu-fu-fu-gan-ran-xin-guan-bing-du-niu-yue-gu-shi-xia-die-1501952|accessdate=2020-10-03|work=www.trt.net.tr|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2021-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210116042131/https://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/cai-jing/2020/10/03/te-lang-pu-fu-fu-gan-ran-xin-guan-bing-du-niu-yue-gu-shi-xia-die-1501952|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

