n.com/sd/202010/t20201005_2407810.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=特朗普清晨在医院发出一堆推特：投票，投票，投票！-侨报网|url=http://www.uschinapress.com/static/content/DX/2020-10-05/762765084916457472.html|accessdate=2020-10-06|work=www.uschinapress.com|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220111455/http://www.uschinapress.com/static/content/DX/2020-10-05/762765084916457472.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

